comments.body:
@IISResetMe Either in this or the next PR, we should probably look at adding ETS members to the input items, similar to how `Get-Content` does it.

This way, in the switch cases you could use `$_` to refer to the line string, but `$_.File` (or similar) to refer to the file the string comes from.

Not sure if you had this planned, but I think it makes sense to have, especially when we start looking at permitting multiple files to come back. 😄
